.TH "LIGHTNING-INVOICE-STATUS" 1 "May 2026" "lightning 0.6.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
lightning-invoice-status \- check whether a local invoice has been paid
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B lightning invoice-status
.I payment_hash|label
.SH DESCRIPTION
Looks up a local BOLT-11 invoice by payment hash or label and returns
its payment status.
.PP
Output:
.nf
{"payment_hash":"...","label":"...","status":"paid|unpaid|expired",
 "amount_msat":N,"paid_at":"ISO8601|null"}
.fi
Returns
.nf
{"error":"not_found"}
.fi
when no matching invoice exists.
.SH EXIT STATUS
.TP
.B 0
Always.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR lightning-invoice-list (1),
.BR lightning-invoice-decode (1)
